SUMMARY:Leron Borsten (University of Hertfordshire), Higher symmetries and homotopy algebras: scattering amplitudes, colour‚Äìkinematics duality, L‚àû‚Äê and BV‚óΩÔ∏è‚àû‚Äêalgebras, the double copy and M2‚Äêbranes models
DESCRIPTION:The string of (possibly cryptic) words in the title will be discussed. Neither prior knowledge of, nor interest in, all of the terms is assumed. We hope there is something for everyone! Essentially, two currently pervasive ideas that we find interesting will be brought together:
